00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:52,610
any other package you need
to use for your Python code

492
00:20:52,610 --> 00:20:55,530
to execute, that would be
wrapped into your layer.

493
00:20:55,530 --> 00:20:59,900
So if you have more than
75 gigbytes of storage

494
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:03,620
necessary for all
of that, then you

495
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:06,990
